title: What Janna has over the other supports?
body:
I dont find her so bad like this forum is claiming, again, i am bronze, so my opinion might differ

Alistar? Brick wall bull with an annoying knock move

Blitz? Biggest bottom lane tilter

Soraka? Sister of teemo, but with heals

Tahm/Thresh? Free out of jail card

Annie? thank gods shes uncommon there, Burst+Stun

Taric? Biggest Brick wall and... a 1 second stun, thats about it

Braum? SHIELDDDDDD

Leona? SHIELLDDD, and sun :^)

What did i missed?
